Building EtherCryptoCoin

See doc/readme-qt.md for instructions on building EtherCryptoCoin-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of EtherCryptoCoin.

See doc/build-*.md for instructions on building ethercryptocoind,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of EtherCryptoCoin.